You guys will get through this and I hope you all accomplish everything you hope for. ♥️💕

snippet.textDisplay:
I'll miss you so much, Dani. I wish you the best of luck in your new career and I'm sure you'll find success and happiness outside of the band as you did in it for these 10 years. Shall you ever decide to come back, we're all be here to welcome you back with arms wide open. You are my favorite Cimorelli sister (no shade to you other Cimorelli gorgeous and talented ladies.)

And I know, I know from the bottom of my heart that you'll do great, as they will too. Please show up every once in a while for us to know you're okay, or please ask your lovely sisters to give us updates on you and your path to success. It won't be easy, life is hard, but that's how we grow, and you're a tough cookie, and you have an amazing family to support you. You'll do great, you incredible human being!

I'm heartbroken to see you leave, and I know all your sisters, your fans and yourself are too. We all love you. Make sure you'll find happiness, please, every day of your life, even if in small things.

I'll see your name again. As the new you. And I will be so proud of you, Dani! We all will, as we did throughout the years in the band. You have amazing and supportive sisters, but we will always be rooting for you too. We all saw you grow up into the incredible woman you are today, and I can speak for myself saying that, despite you won't be here for the videos, you will be out there, fighting for your own dreams. It was a hard decision, but you need to be yourself and pursue what you want your life to be and all every one of us need to do is to understand and never forget you and keep wishing you the best in the world,

I know I'm rambling but it's so hard to see you go... I'm sure we'll see you blossom in your new career, and that your hard work and this sacrifice won't be worthless. We will see your work soon, I know you'll give all of you to this new chapter in your life and the seeds you are now planting are going to turn into beautiful flowers and fruits.


I'm sorry. I teared up... You'll be missed. We love you.
